'''Suprema''' was a title of unknown meaning among the [[Shimholt]] [[Species/Legends|species]] of [[Kar'a'katok]]. The only known Shimholt to hold this title was [[Suprema|Ampotem Za]], who took it as his name upon leaving his [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]].

